Class DatasourceTable

All Implemented Interfaces:
com.fluidops.ajax.components.ReloadableModel, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class DatasourceTable
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
implements com.fluidops.ajax.components.ReloadableModel

Table model to maintain data sources and their distributions. Allows adding LOD data with a single click using RDFProvider or FedX on the fly integration mechanisms.

Data is refreshed on each page load.
